    {
      "id": "text_culture_question",
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Question: 'What kind of team culture do we want to be known for in 2 years, and what is one thing we should start doing tomorrow to get there?'",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 410,
      "width": 1050,
      "style": { "fontSize": 13, "fontWeight": "bold", "color": "#AD1457" }
    },
    {
      "id": "text_culture_host",
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Table Host: Aisha K.",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 470,
      "width": 400,
      "style": { "fontSize": 12, "color": "#607D8B" }
    },
    {
      "id": "text_culture_r1",
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Round 1",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 200,
      "style": { "fontSize": 16, "fontWeight": "bold", "color": "#4A148C" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r1_1",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "We want to be known for trust and transparency — people can disagree openly without fear.",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 530,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F8BBD0", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r1_2",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Start: Monthly 'Ask Me Anything' with leadership. No questions off-limits.",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 530,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F8BBD0", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r1_3",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Innovation time — 10% time for side projects like Google used to do.",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 530,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F8BBD0", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r1_4",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Celebrate failures, not just wins. 'Failure Friday' demos of what we tried and learned.",
      "x": 890,
      "y": 530,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F8BBD0", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "text_culture_r2",
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Round 2",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 620,
      "width": 200,
      "style": { "fontSize": 16, "fontWeight": "bold", "color": "#4A148C" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r2_1",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Cross-team pairing: rotate engineers between teams for 1 sprint/quarter to spread knowledge.",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F48FB1", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r2_2",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Async-first culture. Default to written communication. Meetings need agendas or they get cancelled.",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F48FB1", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r2_3",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Onboarding buddy system — every new hire gets a peer buddy (not their manager) for first 90 days.",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F48FB1", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r2_4",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Psychological safety survey every quarter. Act on results visibly.",
      "x": 890,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F48FB1", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "text_culture_r3",
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Round 3",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 740,
      "width": 200,
      "style": { "fontSize": 16, "fontWeight": "bold", "color": "#4A148C" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r3_1",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Recognition should be peer-driven, not just top-down. Shout-out channel in Slack with monthly highlights.",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 770,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#CE93D8", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r3_2",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Work-life boundaries: no Slack after 6 PM as a team norm. Lead by example from management.",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 770,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#CE93D8", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r3_3",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "The 'tomorrow' answer: start with a weekly 15-min culture check-in during retros.",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 770,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#CE93D8", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_c1r3_4",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Document team values explicitly. Vote on top 5. Print and post them.",
      "x": 890,
      "y": 770,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#CE93D8", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
