      "id": "sticky_p1r1_2",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "AI should be the differentiator. Every feature should have an 'AI-powered' angle.",
      "x": 2750,
      "y": 530,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#A5D6A7", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_p1r1_3",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Speed matters. If our tool is not faster than the alternatives, AI does not matter.",
      "x": 3020,
      "y": 530,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#A5D6A7", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky_p1r1_4",
      "type": "sticky_note",
      "content": "Focus on 10-50 person teams. Don't chase enterprise yet. Win the mid-market first.",
      "x": 3290,
      "y": 530,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 70,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#A5D6A7", "textAlign": "left", "fontSize": 10 }
